{"chapters": {"ch01-o-gene-como-unidade": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A EVOLUÇÃO VISTA DO PONTO DE VISTA DO GENE</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">O GENE</span> <span class=\"bd\">EGOÍSTA</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Richard Dawkins</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 32a6 6 0 1 1 6 6 12 12 0 1 1-12-12 18 18 0 1 1 18 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Replicador × Veículo</div><div class=\"card-body\">O <strong>replicador</strong> (o gene) é a informação copiada que persiste por gerações; o <strong>veículo</strong> (o organismo) é a máquina mortal que o abriga e propaga. O corpo morre; o gene é potencialmente <em>imortal</em>.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> ao explicar uma adaptação, separe o que é replicador (persiste e é copiado) do que é veículo (efêmero).</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 10L54 22 32 34 10 22 32 10z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M10 32l22 12 22-12M10 42l22 12 22-12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Máquina de Sobrevivência</div><div class=\"card-body\">Todo organismo é um robô construído pelos genes para abrigá-los. 'Eles nos criaram, corpo e mente.' Os genes não controlam em tempo real — <strong>programam</strong> estratégias que o cérebro executa sozinho.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> gene = programador; animal = programa rodando, autônomo na execução mas com objetivos herdados.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M48 14C28 14 14 28 14 48c20 0 34-14 34-34z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 42L42 22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Os Três Trunfos do Replicador</div><div class=\"card-body\">O replicador bem-sucedido maximiza <strong>longevidade</strong> (durar), <strong>fecundidade</strong> (copiar muito) e <strong>fidelidade</strong> (copiar com precisão). A vida começou com uma molécula que, por acaso, fazia cópias de si no caldo primordial.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> evolução é, no fundo, 'sobrevivência dos estáveis' — quem persiste, prevalece.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 10v40M18 50h28\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 20h36\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 20l-6 12a7 7 0 0 0 12 0L14 20zM50 20l-6 12a7 7 0 0 0 12 0L50 20z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Falácia do 'Bem da Espécie'</div><div class=\"card-body\">Animais não agem 'para preservar a espécie' — a <strong>seleção de grupo</strong> é instável: um mutante egoísta invade e domina o grupo altruísta. A seleção atua muito abaixo: no gene.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Regra:</strong> ao ouvir 'isso evoluiu para o bem da espécie', desconfie e reformule no nível do gene.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch02-parentesco-e-altruismo": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A EVOLUÇÃO VISTA DO PONTO DE VISTA DO GENE</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">O GENE</span> <span class=\"bd\">EGOÍSTA</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Richard Dawkins</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M26 38l12-12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 32l-6 6a8 8 0 0 0 11 11l6-6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M42 32l6-6a8 8 0 0 0-11-11l-6 6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Seleção de Parentesco</div><div class=\"card-body\">Genes de altruísmo dirigido a <strong>parentes</strong> se espalham porque os parentes tendem a carregar os mesmos genes. O laço de sangue não importa por si — importa o <strong>gene compartilhado</strong> que ele sinaliza.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> trate parentes como bancos parciais dos seus genes — ajudar um irmão é 'investir meio você mesmo'.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Regra de Hamilton (rB > C)</div><div class=\"card-body\">Um gesto altruísta evolui quando <strong>r × B > C</strong>: <em>r</em> = grau de parentesco, <em>B</em> = benefício ao receptor, <em>C</em> = custo ao doador. Haldane: 'eu morreria por dois irmãos ou oito primos'.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> estime r, B e C — se o produto rB excede C, o altruísmo tende a se fixar.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 56V34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 34L16 14M32 34l16-20\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"48\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Grau de Parentesco (r)</div><div class=\"card-body\">r é a probabilidade de o parente carregar o mesmo gene: <strong>½</strong> para irmãos e pais–filhos, <strong>¼</strong> para tios e avós, <strong>⅛</strong> para primos, <strong>1</strong> para gêmeos idênticos. O cuidado se gradua pela proximidade.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> r é uma probabilidade genética, não um sentimento — por isso o altruísmo é desigual entre parentes e estranhos.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"20\" r=\"10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M14 52c0-10 8-18 18-18s18 8 18 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Conflito Dentro do Laço</div><div class=\"card-body\">Como o parentesco é parcial (r<1), os interesses divergem mesmo entre quem se ama: <strong>pais × filhos</strong> (cada filho quer mais que a parte justa), <strong>machos × fêmeas</strong> (quem investe mais é mais 'explorável'). O laço é cooperação <em>e</em> conflito.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> o choro do filhote pode ser sinal honesto OU manipulação para extrair mais investimento.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch03-estrategias-estaveis": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A EVOLUÇÃO VISTA DO PONTO DE VISTA DO GENE</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">O GENE</span> <span class=\"bd\">EGOÍSTA</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Richard Dawkins</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 10v40M18 50h28\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 20h36\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 20l-6 12a7 7 0 0 0 12 0L14 20zM50 20l-6 12a7 7 0 0 0 12 0L50 20z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Estratégia Evolutivamente Estável (EEE)</div><div class=\"card-body\">Uma estratégia que, adotada pela maioria, <strong>não pode ser invadida</strong> por nenhuma alternativa rara. É um <strong>equilíbrio</strong>, não um ótimo coletivo — pode ser ruim para todos e ainda assim estável.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Teste:</strong> imagine a população toda numa estratégia + um mutante raro; se resiste à invasão, é EEE.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M44 12l8 8-22 22-8-8 22-22z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 42l-8 8M12 44l8 8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Falcão × Pomba</div><div class=\"card-body\">'Falcão' sempre luta; 'Pomba' exibe e recua. Nenhum é EEE puro — a população estabiliza numa <strong>mistura</strong> dos dois. Mostra por que o mundo animal não é nem todo agressivo nem todo pacífico.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> pense em comportamento social como jogo — o que compensa depende do que os outros fazem.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M6 38c6-8 12-8 18 0s12 8 18 0 12-8 16 0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M6 26c6-8 12-8 18 0s12 8 18 0 12-8 16 0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Altruísmo Recíproco</div><div class=\"card-body\">Cooperação entre <strong>não-parentes</strong> evolui quando os encontros se repetem e há memória: 'você coça minhas costas, eu coço as suas'. Exige reencontro, reconhecimento e detecção de trapaceiro.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Regra:</strong> sem repetição nem memória, a traição é estável — não conte com cooperação espontânea.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 52h12V40h12V28h12V16h8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Olho por Olho: Os Bonzinhos em 1º</div><div class=\"card-body\">No torneio de Axelrod (dilema do prisioneiro iterado), vence <strong>Olho por Olho</strong>: gentil (não trai primeiro), retaliador (pune na hora), perdoador (volta a cooperar) e claro. Em relações repetidas, a gentileza condicional é a estratégia robusta.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> maximize o ganho mútuo, não a diferença para o rival — a inveja piora seu resultado.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "ch04-memes-e-alcance": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">A EVOLUÇÃO VISTA DO PONTO DE VISTA DO GENE</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">O GENE</span> <span class=\"bd\">EGOÍSTA</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Richard Dawkins</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"14\" cy=\"16\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"48\" cy=\"48\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"16\" cy=\"48\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 28L16 18M37 29l11-9M37 36l9 10M27 36l-9 10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Meme</div><div class=\"card-body\"><strong>Termo cunhado neste livro:</strong> a unidade de transmissão cultural (ideia, melodia, moda, crença) que se replica de cérebro a cérebro por imitação, sujeita à sua própria seleção. Memes competem por <strong>atenção e memória</strong>.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> pense em ideias como organismos competindo por mentes — vence quem se copia melhor, não quem é verdadeiro.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M6 32s10-16 26-16 26 16 26 16-10 16-26 16S6 32 6 32z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Complexo de Memes (Memeplex)</div><div class=\"card-body\">Memes que se reforçam e se propagam <strong>em conjunto</strong> — como doutrinas e ideologias. Um memeplex pode ser <strong>parasitário</strong>, espalhando-se mesmo contra o interesse de quem o carrega.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> 'bom para o meme' ≠ 'bom para você', assim como 'bom para o gene' ≠ 'bom para o indivíduo'.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"22\" r=\"12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M30 30l22 22M44 44l6-6M38 50l6-6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Fenótipo Estendido</div><div class=\"card-body\">Os efeitos de um gene <strong>não param na pele</strong>: a represa do castor, o ninho do pássaro, a teia da aranha e até a <strong>manipulação do hospedeiro</strong> por um parasita são fenótipos do gene, agindo no mundo exterior. O gene alcança longe.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> apague a 'pele' como limite causal — o alcance do gene vai até onde chegam seus efeitos.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Rebelião Contra os Genes</div><div class=\"card-body\">Somos a única espécie capaz de <strong>prever</strong> e <strong>resistir</strong> à lógica dos genes (e dos memes) egoístas. Podemos cultivar altruísmo genuíno e cooperação deliberada. 'Temos o poder de nos voltar contra nossos criadores.'</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Lembrete do autor:</strong> descrever como a seleção opera NÃO é endossá-la como ética — cuidado com a falácia naturalista.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"]}}